    "description": "<p>Effect: Connection – Barrier. When the user declares Barrier, they may spend 3 PP as a Free Action at @Trait[interrupt-3] to gain +1 SPDEF Stage for 5 Activations and @Tick[6 shield]. When the user would be targeted by an Attack, the user may spend 4 PP as a Free Action at @Trait[interrupt-4] to freely use Barrier, gain @Affliction[braced 3], and be Flinched 4.</p>",
